node.text: today I’m sharing the new @OralB iO with you guys and it SERIOUSLY is my fav toothbrush EVER. It has this cute little two minute timer to hit the dentist recommended time AND is smart as hell with it’s own BLUETOOTH. It gives you a score and tells you what you’re missing! ARE YOU KIDDING ME?! I got a 91 😎 Also, Oral-B is donating a total of $1 million of product and dental care to Dental Lifeline Network to help high risk individuals - so important right now! So I’m pretty proud to be partnering with a brand making a difference - check the Oral-B iO out for yourself now and experience the #OralBWOW! learn more at oralb.com

node.text: hey guys so i posted this to my stories a few days ago... but stories disappear after 24 hours and i want to ALWAYS remember this moment. since i’ve posted this, Derek Chauvin has been arrested and charged with 3rd degree murder (absolutely not good enough in my opinion) and the other 3 officers have still yet to be charged. millions of people, including myself, have signed petitions and donated to this cause. massive peaceful protestors have gathered in major cities to show solidarity and unity (many have been disrupted by police, escalating to violence and police brutality) WE WILL MAKE A DIFFERENCE, our voices will be heard and we will be seen. please stay safe out there ✊🏻✊🏼✊🏽✊🏾✊🏿

node.text: it’s been a JOURNEY 🙃

HAPPY BIRTHDAY BESTIE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! to my fellow fool @larlarlee i love you so so so much and i hope you have the most amazing birthday! so lucky and blessed to have you in my life! feels like we’ve been friends for 20 years… can’t wait for another 20! you truly are one of the best people i’ve ever met in my entire life snd i’m so grateful to have you in mine ❤️
